main event: A UFO was observed by an AF interceptor pilot in Guam on December 31, 1956.
interesting points: The UFO passed under the pilot's aircraft and then came over the pilot again,The UFO was described as dime-size with blinking white lights,The pilot was unable to gain contact with the object, The sighting lasted for about 10 minutes, The case is classified as UNIDENTIFIED pending further details.
